/bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=43563096&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">yone0000 发表于 2019-5-4 16:52</font></a><br />\nhttps://lineblog.me/toyamanao/archives/9373467.html</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/068.png\" />太真实了","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"8","replycredit":"0","position":"12169","username":"傘木希美","adminid":"0","groupid":"31","memberstatus":"0","number":"11877","dbdateline":"1556960276","groupiconid":"7"},{"pid":"43563484","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"abc19950913","authorid":"491082","dateline":"2019-5-4 17:23","message":"<font color=\"#5c5c5c\">忙里偷闲画个夏纪和优子，本来打算清下原画再加个动画，但工作的原画还没画完，还是等有空再说吧</font><img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/067.png\" />顺便放个p站id=74554830<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"https://img.saraba1st.com/forum/201905/04/172131iv6p12777pgq7p7w.png\" attach=\"43563484\" /></div><br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"12170","username":"abc19950913","adminid":"0","groupid":"31","memberstatus":"0","number":"11878","dbdateline":"1556961796","attachments":[],"imagelist":[],"groupiconid":"7"},{"pid":"43563971","tid":"1336553","first":"0","author":"ggqude","authorid":"200071","dateline":"2019-5-4 18:05","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=43557799&amp;ptid=1336553\"><font color=\"#999999\">星野航 发表于 2019-5-4 01:53</font></a><br />\r\n这样的故事描述，大概懂了，如果说展现出了のぞみぞ关系最坏的一种可能性，倒不如说是展示出了武田对两个 ...</div><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/026.png\" />您这么一说，确实。对比原作和动画能感觉到很多角色原本身上的棱角、尖锐的部分在动画里都被巧妙地剔除了（青鸟算保留得比较多了）。当然动画也可能是考虑到目标客层和作品基调的缘故才做出这样的改动（青鸟是山田的私货）。原作中的のぞみぞ之间的互相不信任在青鸟里被稀释了许多，或许像その日里那样极端地心意丝毫不相同才是武田的本意吧。不过原作和青鸟我都很喜欢就是了她们的关系怎么样已经不重要了我只希望她们至少能各自幸福<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/139.png\"